comment: Outstanding experience! The car was spotless and performed perfectly. Highly recommend this model.
Good service overall. Car was clean, but pickup took 15 minutes longer than expected.
Excellent! Car was in perfect condition, staff very professional. Will rent again.
Disappointed. Car had engine noise from day one. Had to return early – got refund but inconvenient.
Decent car, but interior had some wear and wasn't fully cleaned. Drove well though.
Luxury car lived up to expectations. Smooth ride and great features. Worth the price.
Terrible experience! Car broke down on highway. Waited 3 hours for assistance. Never again.
Reliable car for long trip. No issues, good fuel economy. Staff helpful at return.
Second time renting this car – always reliable and comfortable. Great value!
Perfect for family trip. Spacious, safe, and well-maintained. 10/10 would rent again.
